summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting a (\*\*\*) franchise from King County to Construct, maintain, and operate sanitary sewers within certain road and street rights of way located in King County, Washington (\*\*\*) as herein more particularly set forth for the Empire Way South and South Victor Street Sanitary Sewer Projects and authorizing and directing the City Engineer to execute said franchise for and on behalf of the city of Seattle.
